bug.short_desc: Menu drop down overlaps menu bar
bug.cf_doc_type: If docs needed, set a value

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 1246598 Screenshot
Description of problem: The menu drop-down overlaps the menu bar. Makes it impossible to navigate to the right item on the bar. See attachment.
Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable): 3.22.1
How reproducible: Click any menu item
Steps to Reproduce: 1.Click any menu item 2. 3.
Actual results: Menu drop-down overlaps the menu bar
Expected results: Menu drop-down to be positioned below the menu bar
Additional info:
The problem has been fixed. The menu now drops nicely below the menu bar again.
